last_episode_to_air.name: Grand Finale
last_episode_to_air.overview: It’s time to crown a winner! Our finalists go head-to-head and toe-to-toe as they fight to be crowned America's Next Celebrity Drag Race Superstar.

name: Secret Celebrity RuPaul's Drag Race
overview: Secret celebrities - from all walks of life - compete in full drag as they try to impress Emmy Award winning host, RuPaul. To save themselves from elimination, they have to lip sync for their lives. In the end, one celebrity will be crowned America's Next Celebrity Drag Superstar.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Queen Supremes Trixie Mattel, Bob The Drag Queen and Monet X Change make over Nico Tortorella, Jordan Connor and Jermaine Fowler before the celebs compete in Snatch Game.

episodes.overview: Queen Supremes Alyssa Edwards, Asia O'Hara and Trinity The Tuck drag up Loni Love, Tami Roman and Vanessa Williams for their performances in a "9 to 5"-inspired musical.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Queen Supremes Bob The Drag Queen, Kim Chi and Nina West give drag makeovers to celebrity guests Alex Newell, Dustin Milligan and Matt Iseman for The Roast of RuPaul.

guest_stars.character: Self - Special Guest / Madam That Bitch
guest_stars.name: Alex Newell

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: In this conclusion to the four part special event, three new celebrities step inside the workroom to form a fierce glam rock-inspired pop group sensation. Queens Supremes Alyssa Edwards, Monique Heart and Vanessa Vangie Mateo drag up Hayley Kiyoko, Madison Beer and Phoebe Robinson.

guest_stars.character: Self - Special Guest / Queen Eleza Beth
guest_stars.name: Hayley Kiyoko

episodes.name: I’m Coming Out - First Time in Drag!
episodes.overview: Nine mystery celebrities hit the stage for the first time as they debut their new dragged-up personas in live musical performances and start their journey towards the crown.

episodes.name: Dance Your Padded Ass Off!
episodes.overview: The competition continues as the mystery queens incorporate famous dance numbers into show-stopping lip sync performances, and another contestant's secret identity is revealed.

episodes.name: Money Honey
episodes.overview: The mystery celebrities give priceless lip sync performances inspired by Dolly Parton, bling and Benjamins, and one more star gets eliminated.

episodes.name: Drag Duets
episodes.overview: Six RuPaul's Drag Race legends arrive to perform divine duets with remaining contestants Donna Bellissima, Chakra 7, Poppy Love, Thirsty von Trapp, Milli von Sunshine and Chic-Li-Fay.

episodes.name: I Love the 90s
episodes.overview: The queens lip sync to Britney Spears, Spice Girls, Lauryn Hill and more in a tribute to the musical magic of the 90s, and RuPaul introduces a twist that turns the competition on its head.

episodes.name: RuPaul-A-Palooza!
episodes.overview: The five remaining queens reveal their identities and dive into classic Drag Race challenges, including a group musical performance and fierce lip syncs to RuPaul's songs.

episodes.name: Yaaas Gaga
episodes.overview: Don't be a drag just be a queen. Our celebrity drag queens perform songs from the Lady Gaga songbook.

episodes.name: Grand Finale
episodes.overview: It’s time to crown a winner! Our finalists go head-to-head and toe-to-toe as they fight to be crowned America's Next Celebrity Drag Race Superstar.
